menu "Core Library Configuration"

    config HTTP_CLIENT_RESPONSE_BUFFER_SIZE
        int "HTTP client response buffer size (bytes)"
        default 4096
        range 512 32768
        help
            Size of the pre-allocated buffer for HTTP response data.
            This buffer is allocated once at HttpClient construction and
            reused for all requests. Larger buffers allow larger responses
            but consume more RAM.

endmenu
